CodeRED Xenia RDR Pass J / v12 patch summary
=============================================

This patch is intentionally scoped to emulator-side and tooling-side changes.
It does not modify dashboard/system-update XEX or PIRS files.

Changed source
--------------

src/xenia/kernel/XLiveAPI.cc
- Added Netplay cvar:
  DEFINE_bool(netplay_udp_bootstrap, true, ...)

src/xenia/kernel/xam/xam_net.cc
- Declares netplay_udp_bootstrap.
- Adds controlled UDP bootstrap helpers:
  - ShouldInjectUdpBootstrap
  - BuildUdpBootstrapPacket
  - FillUdpBootstrapFrom
  - StoreUdpBootstrapFrom
  - InjectUdpBootstrapPacket
  - InjectUdpBootstrapPacketWSA
- recvfrom / WSARecvFrom behavior:
  - If network mode is LAN/private and the receive would otherwise return
    WSAEWOULDBLOCK / 10035, injects a small local discovery packet on the first
    poll and then at a controlled interval.
  - Logs:
    CodeRED Netplay: UDP bootstrap injected ...
    CodeRED MP correlation: bootstrap packet advertises candidates=...

Changed tools and launchers
---------------------------

tools/codered_rdr_bootstrap_guard_v9.py
- Default RDR search root stays at the current Xenia source tree.
- Adds strict unsafe launch-token filtering:
  system.manifest, su20076000_00000000, FFFE07DF, system/update/dashboard
  default.xex targets.
- Writes netplay_udp_bootstrap = true under [Netplay].

tools/codered_rdr_bootstrap_host_v9.py
- Upgrades runtime behavior to v12 while preserving the existing v9 filename
  and launch menu compatibility.
- Logs to logs/codered_udp_bootstrap_v12.log.
- Replies directly to observed UDP peers and advertises MP script candidates.

tools/codered_collect_v12.py
- New small-log collector and MP/network correlation reporter.
- Produces logs/codered_v12_mp_correlation.txt/json.
- Excludes .dmp files and large logs from the send bundle.

tools/codered_xenia_netplay_smoke.py
- Adds v12 marker checks for netplay_udp_bootstrap, UDP bootstrap injection,
  the v12 collector, and the Pass J doc.

Batch wrappers
--------------

CodeRED_Build_Xenia_Release_v3.bat
- New Release build wrapper.
- Resolves Visual Studio bundled CMake when cmake.exe is not on PATH.

CodeRED_Start_RDR_BootstrapHost_v9.bat
- Starts the upgraded v12 UDP/bootstrap behavior and writes the v12 UDP log.

CodeRED_RDR_Bootstrap_Menu_v9.bat
- Option 8 now collects v12 small logs and MP correlation.

CodeRED_Collect_Small_Logs_v9.bat
- Also runs the v12 collector for compatibility.

CodeRED_Collect_Small_Logs_v12.bat
- New direct v12 collector wrapper.

